css can be added in three major ways
    1. inline css writing css inside the tag itself
    2. internal css writing css inside head tag
    3. external css adding a external .css file into the html file 
some more things to remember while writing css
    1. pref is given to the last css added tag
    2. to make one css overwrite all others just write !important instinde the semicolon
    3. inline css >> inside css

